results.name: Write A064476(n) = 2^i(n)*3^j(n); sequence gives values of i(n).
program: (ARIBAS): function a064514(maxarg: integer); var j: integer; ar: array; begin ar := p2p3(maxarg); for j := 0 to maxarg - 1 do write(ar[j][1]," "); end; end; a064514(85). For definition of function p2p3 see A064476.
